OL,3,CSunderland and Ireland legend Charlie
OL,4,C'The King' Hurley dies aged 87
OL,6,FSunderland AFC has paid tribute to
OL,7,Fformer player Charlie Hurley,
OL,8,Fdescribed as a 'giant' in the story of
OL,9,Fthe club, after his death was
OL,10,Fannounced on Thursday.
OL,12,FHurley passed away at the age of 88.
OL,13,FKnown affectionately as 'the King' on
OL,14,FWearside, he was named as the club's
OL,15,FPlayer of the Century in 1979, having
OL,16,Fmade more than 400 appearances for the
OL,17,Fclub.
