OL,6,FIt was to be the start of twelve
OL,7,Fmemorable years on Wearside in which
OL,8,Fhe cemented his place in the hearts of
OL,9,Fsupporters, who hailed him as 'the
OL,10,Fgreatest centre-half the world has
OL,11,Fever seen'. He captained the side to
OL,12,Fpromotion in the 1963-64 season,
OL,13,Fappearing in all but one game.
OL,15,FA proud Irishman, he amassed 40
OL,16,Finternational caps with 38 of those
OL,17,Fcoming during his time at Sunderland.
